{"tid":425752,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果App Store等多部主機癱瘓中，多項服務將受到影響","createTime":"2017-10-06T04:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T12:57:50.000Z","uid":83012,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"57d33bb1de3c81a458140b873532bf813a321f72","tid":425752,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/121427_b179beb99f7918b1c03ae028114da0e9.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F121427_b179beb99f7918b1c03ae028114da0e9.PNG&h=3e48757e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日蘋果（Apple）多項系統服務出現故障情形，導致App Store、Apple Music、iTunes Store等服務將會有少數用戶受到影響<br />\n<br />\n目前從蘋果官網系統狀態上可得知，從今日（6）上午1:52開始，有多項服務目前會導致有些用戶無法正常使用，目前還尚未恢復正常，如面臨App無法更新或下載使用，請等待修復完成就能繼續使用該服務<br />\n<br />\nApp Store<br />\nApple Music<br />\nApple TV<br />\niTunes Store<br />\niTunes U<br />\nMac App Store<br />\n大量採購計畫<br />\n雲端iTunes"},{"pid":"c8cf3dff7b32026381f56fb00b55e16a4c92b290","tid":425752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8851771ff7a041aeab615e03daad0d6af6c1056a","tid":425752,"uid":8048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"apple 已死"},{"pid":"db1f9bc00471cb1f2da53394576eb1a25e302f65","tid":425752,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"全球（包括香港）回收晒啲iphone 未？"},{"pid":"ab04941a2ef53b5c42d3422f502041f2457d64d4","tid":425752,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/122945_fcf6e794dfc66d6b7574708b142a5fdb.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F122945_fcf6e794dfc66d6b7574